Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.32,0:00:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.91,0:00:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有證人在場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.29,0:00:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.20,0:00:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是... 不認識的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.75,0:00:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.85,0:00:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都說到這種地步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.21,0:00:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才是真的不在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.72,0:00:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 這張卡片放在了比我原來埋得更深的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.88,0:00:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都覺得很不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.63,0:00:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同學為甚麼要選她做妹妹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.46,0:00:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣沒甚麼特點的平凡學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.32,0:00:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她與祥子同學一點也不相襯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.06,0:01:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集在瑪莉亞的庭院裡的少女們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.62,0:01:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也帶著天使般無垢的笑容 穿越與身同高的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.09,0:01:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覆蓋住純潔身心的是深色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.71,0:01:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要讓裙子的摺痕亂掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.53,0:01:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要讓白色的水手服領結外翻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.71,0:01:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒緩的行走成了這裡的習俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.63,0:01:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私立莉莉安女學園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.22,0:01:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是少女的花園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.06,0:03:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}紅色卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.50,0:03:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早醒來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.18,0:03:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最先浮現在腦中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.03,0:03:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是「今天是情人節」這個事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.24,0:03:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 鵜澤美冬從高中開始進入了莉莉安女學園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.96,0:03:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 與其它的外部應試者稍微有點不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.72,0:03:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前 我曾在莉莉安的幼兒園上過一陣學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.30,0:03:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那時起 祥子同學對我來說就已經是一種特殊的存在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.22,0:03:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貴安 美冬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.96,0:03:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貴安 友子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.11,0:03:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貴安 祥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.00,0:03:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貴安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.32,0:04:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同學擁有著與他人不同的某種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.29,0:04:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可說是天生而來的 某種令人難以接近的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.72,0:04:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是繪畫 還是跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.68,0:04:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同學都不會輸給任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.44,0:04:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳得真好 祥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.68,0:04:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即使受到誇獎 她也並未與其它人變得更親近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.41,0:04:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂小孩子 就是會對擁有與自已不同氣質的人而感到敏感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.65,0:04:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於同班同學所投射過來的驚奇的目光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.67,0:04:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同學毫不在意地只以沉鬱的表情無視掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.89,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同學在無言地戰鬥著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.90,0:05:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為同班同學某句無心的話 她開始換乘班車來上學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.38,0:05:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是讓車送到離自已家最近的候車點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再從那裡乘上班車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用了這種費勁的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.67,0:05:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而平凡的我的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.37,0:05:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻不可遏制地追尋著\N那樣的祥子同學在平常的點點滴滴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.40,0:05:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那份幸福並未持續多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在父親的調職決定後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.82,0:05:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也即將離開莉莉安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就不能再看到祥子同學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.31,0:05:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時的我 也並非是覺得與祥子同學分別很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.33,0:05:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因無法再看到祥子同學\n而感覺到深深的遺憾而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.64,0:06:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美冬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.13,0:06:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美冬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.87,0:06:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀～ 是血 不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.44,0:06:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得趕快叫老師來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.98,0:06:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.75,0:06:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.87,0:06:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.81,0:06:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在幹甚麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.17,0:06:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.57,0:06:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因為不聽老師的囑咐才會受到懲罰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.94,0:06:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了在從鞦韆上跌下來前\N所看到的祥子同學那不愉快的表情的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.06,0:06:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為站著盪鞦韆是被規章所禁止的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.29,0:06:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 手帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.07,0:06:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送給你了 我另外多帶了一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與祥子同學的對話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.73,0:07:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從別人那裡得到甚麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.44,0:07:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些都是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.23,0:07:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久 到了我離開幼兒園的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.81,0:07:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.53,0:07:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說了送給你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.43,0:07:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 媽媽叫我要送還給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.98,0:07:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外還有這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.31,0:07:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.57,0:07:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.86,0:07:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽說這是謝禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.56,0:07:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請替我向美冬的媽媽說聲謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.36,0:07:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我第一次從祥子同學\n的嘴裡聽到自已名字的瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.27,0:07:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.92,0:07:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.26,0:07:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是永別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.70,0:07:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會再回到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會再回到她的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.78,0:07:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見 祥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.28,0:08:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年後 我回到了莉莉安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.41,0:08:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長大後的祥子同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.54,0:08:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是如同聖母瑪莉亞一般優雅而恬靜的女性吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.87,0:08:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我急切地期盼著再會的那一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.29,0:08:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.95,0:08:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在哪裡見過嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.35,0:08:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同學 老師在叫你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.63,0:08:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能暫時失陪一下嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.79,0:08:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.62,0:08:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一刻 我充份地明白了人不是那麼容易改變的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.67,0:08:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她仍舊是全身洋盈著讓他人無法接近的威嚴感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.83,0:08:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我這樣毫無特點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.55,0:08:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連印象也沒法讓她留下的平凡的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.01,0:09:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我與她之間的距離感與十年前完全沒有變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.30,0:09:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是眾多的同班同學中的一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.78,0:09:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久 她成了紅薔薇的花蕾的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.72,0:09:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成了離我更遠的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.88,0:09:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這樣 我也因回到了\N能注視著祥子同學的生活而感到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.71,0:09:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年能交給她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.88,0:09:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概還是交不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.85,0:09:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為去年的情人節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.25,0:09:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.63,0:09:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰的巧克力也沒有接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.22,0:09:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 我不能接受這種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.38,0:09:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我沒有接受的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.92,0:09:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有接受的理由也許就能讓她接受了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.74,0:09:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像那時一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.63,0:10:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.23,0:10:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底想去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了今天的尋寶活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.03,0:10:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在要去將卡片藏在某處！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.14,0:10:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我壓抑不住自已的好奇心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.83,0:11:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是 祥子同學的紅色卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花蕾們到底把卡片藏在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.08,0:11:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是薔薇館最可疑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.21,0:11:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰也不會找到祥子同學的卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.19,0:11:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色的卡片就像是一張王牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.07,0:11:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要怎麼使用全看我的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.77,0:11:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美冬同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.34,0:11:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是今天的值日吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.89,0:11:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.47,0:11:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大森老師不是說過\N「立刻來理科準備室取第五節課要用的資料」嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.11,0:11:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.00,0:11:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美冬同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.85,0:11:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我幫忙嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.77,0:12:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.95,0:12:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一點兒資料我一個人就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.51,0:12:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.58,0:12:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.69,0:12:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到祥子同學的臉後 我變得害怕起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.13,0:12:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把偷偷先找到的卡片\n若無其事地拿到薔薇館去的膽量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.04,0:12:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是沒有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.75,0:12:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果現在放回去的話 還來得及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.35,0:12:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 好不容易才到手的卡片卻...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.55,0:12:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅 白 黃的卡片將分別藏在校內的某處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.42,0:12:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,限制時間是一小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.26,0:12:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到卡片後 請帶回到作為本部的薔薇館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.08,0:12:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著就可獲贈\N作為附加獎的與花蕾們的半天約會權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.50,0:12:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我猶豫的時候 尋寶活動開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.00,0:12:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢啊 我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.86,0:12:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因為想要的東西就擺在眼前 竟未做多想就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.06,0:13:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今 終於理解到自已所做所為的嚴重性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.32,0:13:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 開始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.31,0:13:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須把它放回原來的地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.17,0:13:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 即使還了回去 像這種地方一定不會有人來找的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.76,0:13:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但即便如此 我也沒資格就這樣拿著它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.78,0:13:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼會變成這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.95,0:13:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想要祥子同學回頭看看我而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.93,0:13:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.19,0:13:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因為不聽老師的囑咐才會受到懲罰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.74,0:13:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是受到懲罰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.09,0:13:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我與這張紅色卡片一起 被關在了這個古舊的溫室裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.75,0:13:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.39,0:14:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貴安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 好像嚇到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.80,0:14:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.88,0:14:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是來這裡找卡片嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.72,0:14:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福澤祐巳同學 是祥子同學所選的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.79,0:14:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 祥子同學將隱藏的地點告訴了祐巳同學呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.36,0:14:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是這樣的話 我也能稍微安心一點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.45,0:14:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那些一無所知地尋找祥子同學卡片的人來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.57,0:14:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同學跟我一樣罪孽深重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.05,0:14:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是狗一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.28,0:14:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 像這樣拼命地 幹勁十足地掘著土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說祐巳同學...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.23,0:14:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想卡片應該就在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.54,0:14:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼認真的眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.09,0:14:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同學果然是靠自已的力量找到這裡來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.95,0:14:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便的話 請用這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.02,0:14:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論怎麼挖也無法在那裡找到卡片的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.89,0:15:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但越是把這一結局往後拖延\n我就越覺得自已變得污穢似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.17,0:15:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法再忍耐著看下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那裡沒有卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.80,0:15:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.15,0:15:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我說晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.30,0:15:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上我剛才也挖掘過那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.11,0:15:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.29,0:15:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼會認為卡片在那裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.76,0:15:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.52,0:15:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.71,0:15:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然事前沒有被告知過 那麼祐巳同學是怎麼找到這裡來的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.74,0:15:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這個薔薇就叫做紅薔薇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.10,0:15:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.80,0:15:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是紅薔薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.29,0:15:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同祥子同學的分身般的花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.63,0:15:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以祥子同學才會將卡片藏在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.21,0:15:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 只有祐巳同學察覺到了這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.91,0:15:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全地輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.50,0:16:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明如此的接近 我卻完全未察覺到這種花的含義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.93,0:16:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經到4點40分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.88,0:16:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,參加活動的同學們請立刻到中庭集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.83,0:16:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 祐巳同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.05,0:16:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活動結束了 請立刻到中庭集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.32,0:16:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.49,0:16:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得趕快收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.43,0:16:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來幫你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.56,0:16:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.99,0:16:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直覺得很不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.54,0:16:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 就在這裡分手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.38,0:16:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貴安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.24,0:16:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同學為甚麼會選擇她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.76,0:16:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她與祥子同學一點也不相襯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我擅自地那樣認定著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但通過今天的事我明白了一些東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.79,0:16:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同學擁有著我所沒有的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.47,0:17:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而祥子同學發現了這些東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.47,0:17:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同學的確有看人的眼光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃到「中」的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.83,0:17:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會無一例外地獲贈與我的半天約會權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.75,0:17:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約會？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.45,0:17:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不是 那個 這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.67,0:17:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很有趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.58,0:17:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.59,0:17:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼時候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.49,0:17:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個... 那麼這周的周日如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.47,0:17:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.95,0:17:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.13,0:17:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 你想去哪裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.72,0:17:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去祐巳想去的地方就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.96,0:17:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼讓我先想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.99,0:17:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會期待著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.15,0:17:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.35,0:17:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.55,0:17:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大學入學考試做得還好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.62,0:17:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 今天的估計不大好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.29,0:17:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你反倒是相當的愉快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.79,0:18:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為托了尋寶活動的福 我的願望實現了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.12,0:18:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 就是那個「在畢業之前 我想看看薔薇館裡普通學生們喧鬧的樣子」嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.79,0:18:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 今天是我到目前為止的人生中最好的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.54,0:18:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.31,0:18:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.15,0:18:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.23,0:18:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.50,0:18:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.45,0:18:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我能去您家裡拜訪您嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.17,0:18:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有東西想交給您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.41,0:18:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.18,0:18:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.59,0:18:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼要把卡片藏在那麼奇怪的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.96,0:18:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把卡片夾在「江戶的物價」甚麼的書間 太難明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃 生氣了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.50,0:19:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種話等一會兒再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.28,0:19:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我也會去由乃的家裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.00,0:19:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管你了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.01,0:19:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.72,0:19:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 姐姐 等會兒再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.50,0:19:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也是夾心巧克力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.48,0:19:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是特意送到家裡來的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.93,0:19:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多半是慣例的手製品了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.00,0:19:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.52,0:19:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真冷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.12,0:19:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 從靜那裡得到了酒心巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.30,0:19:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃點暖暖身體嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.93,0:19:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐在某些地方真是有點遲鈍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.88,0:19:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫉妒了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.09,0:19:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.53,0:19:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果讓我拿了專為姐姐而做的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.60,0:19:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜大人會是一種甚麼心情呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.68,0:19:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.40,0:19:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 又給我上了一堂課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.89,0:19:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得很自大的樣子真抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.85,0:19:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能有一個懂事的妹妹我真是幸福啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.33,0:19:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就能輕鬆坦然地...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.72,0:20:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 請不要這樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.62,0:20:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果姐姐不在的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.40,0:20:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.89,0:20:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.54,0:20:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了春天 志摩子也會成為二年級生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新生入學後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.32,0:20:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再察覺時 我的離開也就變得很平常了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一點都不覺得會是那麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.24,0:20:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.75,0:20:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大理石花紋巧克力蛋糕 真是非常好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.39,0:20:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又開始下雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.91,0:21:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.88,0:21:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 有關本周日的事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.38,0:21:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉 能請你先回教室嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.15,0:21:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 祥子同學的縫紉箱就先放在我這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.42,0:21:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以拜託你嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.81,0:21:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我會先放在祥子同學的桌上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.05,0:21:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.99,0:21:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟姐姐慢慢地談吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.06,0:21:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 周日的事是？
